name: Glitch Entity #001
description: The pulsating network mainframe remained under the control of the strange being nesting inside both its physical and software cores. Despite the efforts to rid their Site 17 of the anomalous entity, it resisted all forms of attack, both by hackers attempting to break past its living firewalls, as well as the ground team with the site's built in defenses. A collaboration with sosogutter. SIZE: 12x12 inches (300PPI)
